Package: RTraCe
Type: Package
Encoding: UTF-8
Title: Read and plot TraCeR results
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Tomás", "Gomes", email = "tomas.pc.gomes@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Tomás Gomes <tomas.pc.gomes@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides an interface to efficiently read TraCeR output and articulate
    it with other data (optionally with scater). It also includes functions for plotting
    clonotype relationships and interactive visualization using a Shiny App.
